      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/a-propos" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-3 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-sm">
